HEADWORD: munja
<hw>munja</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A tough
Asiatic grass (<spn>Saccharum bengalense</spn> syn. <spn>Saccharum
munja</spn>) whose culms are used for ropes and baskets.</def>⟦br⟧
